Package ScheduleModel

Class Room

  • Object
    • ScheduleModel.Room
  • public class Room
extends Object
    This class describes a classroom with the properties of its:
         • Name (unique Name, can't be the same for multiple rooms)
         • Size
         • Equipments

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      Room​(String Name)
      This constructor only gives a user defined value to the Name
